  "comments": "<p>UV activity: Value in box fluoresce yellow. Beetle wings and trees fluoresce orange.<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64ecf9eb929cf.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64ecf9eb929cf.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Security thread:</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Windowed into six sections on the reverse side, when seen under a backlight, the inscription of “CBVS 10” is repeated throughout.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/66f48dc3b333b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/66f48dc3b333b.jpg\"></a><br>© Kiet Tran</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><br>P#147, signature Henk Goedschalk - President of the Central Bank of Suriname from January 1985 until January 1994; and from January 1997 until August 2000.</p>",
